{"id":36367,"date":"2021-05-28T06:28:05","date_gmt":"2021-05-28T02:28:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=36367"},"modified":"2021-05-28T06:28:05","modified_gmt":"2021-05-28T02:28:05","slug":"afterlife-no-mawt","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/28\/afterlife-no-mawt\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Akhirah: No death in Hereafter, only eternity"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>When the people of Paradise will be sent to Paradise, and the people of Hellfire will be sent to Hellfire, until they are separated between them. Then, death will be slaughtered and a heavenly caller will announce: O people of Paradise, there is no death! O people of Hellfire, there is no death! For the people of Paradise, it will add joy to their joy, and for the people of Hellfire, it will add grief to their grief.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2850<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Muslim<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e <strong>\u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0635\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0629\u0650 \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0629\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0647\u0652\u